  text: Done — I updated `results/runs/ITSM_B_v0_mask_R5_5.4/eval_r3/eval_32093_tc1/output.xlsx`.

I wrote this formula into `F2:F15`:

```excel
=IF(COUNTIF(C2:E2,"<>")=0,B2,IF(COUNTIF(C2:E2,"<>")=1,INDEX(C2:E2,1,MATCH(TRUE,C2:E2<>"",0)),"ERROR"))
```

This does the following:
- if `C:E` are all blank, use the current employee from `B`
- if exactly one of `C:E` has a name, return that name
